When you open the app, you will write your name.
Background color is purple.
When you start the game, the scoreboard will be at the top right. Thhe top left will show the question number and total number of questions.
The center will show the question, and under the question, there will be 4 answer choices.
After all questions have been displayed, the end screen will be shown and it will display the player's score and the number of questions correct and number of questions missed.
